      "writtenOn": "2021-01-21T00:59:15Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "why not `inherit_realms` or something like that? `extends` implies to me that it would be object(s) of the same type (in this case, buckets). acls and bindings are clearer (they correspond to `acl.entry` and `luci.binding`)",
